keywhiz.api.model

Class SecretSeries

  • java.lang.Object
    • keywhiz.api.model.SecretSeries

  • public abstract class SecretSeries
extends Object
    Maps to entity from secrets table. A secret may have many versions, each with different content, but the versions share common information in a SecretSeries, such as name, description, and metadata. In particular, access control is granted to a SecretSeries and not a specific version in that series. New secret versions in the series will "inherit" the same group associations. One-to-many mapping to SecretContents.
